# Vercel ignore file - exclude large directories from deployment
#
# Patterns use gitignore syntax — bare names (e.g. "electron")
# match at any depth, which silently strips matching dirs from
# the deploy. The bare "electron" entry was excluding both the
# top-level Electron app folder AND app/api/electron/* (every
# desktop-app API route). Pin to repo-root with a leading slash
# to avoid the same footgun on future entries.
node_modules
.next
dist-electron
/electron
*.log
.DS_Store
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

# Keep these if needed, but they might be large
# Uncomment if you need to exclude more
# public/downloads/*
# supabase/migrations/*.sql
